snippet: The United States women’s gymnastics team dazzled during qualifying at the 2015 world championships Saturday in Glasgow, posting the top overall score to cement its status as heavy favorites for a repeat.
abstract: United States women’s gymnastics team achieves best overall score in qualifying round of 2015 world championships.
lead_paragraph: The United States women’s gymnastics team dazzled during qualifying at the 2015 world championships Saturday in Glasgow, posting the top overall score to cement its status as heavy favorites for a repeat.
